{"tid":188245,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"你地有冇買醫保同人壽保","createTime":"2017-04-05T13:56:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-18T07:29:08.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"52a6c77f8c9bf9c513568c42da5d3f4c93622c2c","tid":188245,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T13:56:06.000Z","msg":"屋企人有人入左醫院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n覺得都要幫自己買番份<br />\n<br />\n你地有冇買咩保險？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我唔洗咩儲蓄基金個d <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我自己有投資開<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7078409d7e6ad6cdeb015e4e9ec5c8a1f2e3a10","tid":188245,"uid":55990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T14:20:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e7bef9e7dc8672a54264189ec93cb859e1cb5752","tid":188245,"uid":27025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T14:58:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本來應該有好多agent想pm你<br />\n<br />\n但見你唔要儲蓄plan<br />\n<br />\n我諗佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同問，呢排諗緊買保險，但同事都話買醫療就夠<br />\n<br />\n佢地話儲蓄係廢既，而保險佬係靠儲蓄plan食佣，想知多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"887945a4e1a7e7010bc9331bb7684e659194a978","tid":188245,"uid":93811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T16:03:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屋企人有人入左醫院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n覺得都要幫自己買番份<br />\n<br />\n你地有冇買咩保險？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我唔洗咩儲蓄基金個d <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我自己有投資開<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nChing 如果想了解醫療同人壽保既野 我可以比到D意見你 <br />\nTG:moonchanaxa"},{"pid":"957a8461eae1ad1c91396ff897be851c98f37177","tid":188245,"uid":53798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T16:24:09.000Z","msg":"用公立醫院就唔洗買<br />\n<br />\n如果屋企人計下數買危疾定人壽好<br />\n<br />\n你而家先買醫保不如自己比錢仲好"},{"pid":"e2032b56bdd44b1ac0f764cff28e1573450ce0c5","tid":188245,"uid":59211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T00:23:26.000Z","msg":"人壽保險 係睇你 <br />\nlet say如果你聽日死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你有無啲咩經濟上嘅責任要負<br />\n<br />\nEG.你死左 無人供養到爸爸媽媽<br />\nEG.你供緊層樓 你死左就無人供 <br />\n<br />\n如果你都係一般後生仔 未有樓 <br />\n又未有老婆仔女<br />\n保額200萬嘅定期人壽 ，每月保費$113.4<br />\n頭十年保費不變<br />\n(我喺HSBC online咁買 ，做過下research，其他公司收費都係差唔多)<br />\nHSBC, cigna, ZURICH, Pacific life......<br />\n<br />\n有比錢有保 無比就無保<br />\n假設你嘅責任完左(父母都死左), 咁份險可以唔洗再咁多保額，留少少比人幫你搞身後事就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n除非你 死後經濟責任有大變動(娶左老婆，供緊樓，有兒有女)<br />\n如果唔係 唔洗考慮保終身or加大保額<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e793e44e3bb3dd3454a64baa2f169daf04926fe","tid":188245,"uid":9716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T18:55:33.000Z","msg":"巴打可以隨時搵我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/HKCarInsurance/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2FHKCarInsurance%2F&d=sh6QB3P1ZXxG4EHsBexfbuPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=0f955a7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/HKCarInsurance/</a><br />\n雖然係車保專頁，但小弟其他保險都會做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9e1daefcb57fd1275b231ac44aa82c78c9112d5","tid":188245,"uid":70553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T00:12:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>本來應該有好多agent想pm你<br />\n<br />\n但見你唔要儲蓄plan<br />\n<br />\n我諗佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同問，呢排諗緊買保險，但同事都話買醫療就夠<br />\n<br />\n佢地話儲蓄係廢既，而保險佬係靠儲蓄plan食佣，想知多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你唔想agent有佣賺  又想agent service你 都幾矛盾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁樣你不如銀行買啦  行入分行就買到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aef79af0168d5d013dea339e26e5814616d2729b","tid":188245,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T00:14:58.000Z","msg":"樓主同保險9做媒"},{"pid":"c56df73e5a251a3afdf837012f6ebc1334fe031b","tid":188245,"uid":16637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T00:15:00.000Z","msg":"揀個跟得好既agent好重要"},{"pid":"09039dcc2ce6f27145bc565bcf5f8717e1ee7f40","tid":188245,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T07:49:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>揀個跟得好既agent好重要</blockquote><br />\n有冇得好似旅遊保咁自己買完 有事先去claim錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好驚又有d買完點知話唔包唔包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f30d0d74b7fc2e7490af800d528d39aa0555acdd","tid":188245,"uid":55990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T07:51:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ceec9288430601715d724ccdb2f91d1889c550ab","tid":188245,"uid":99536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T07:51:26.000Z","msg":"無仔無女人壽唔使啦<br />\n危疾就有用"},{"pid":"1ffe6c1cecdbfd4bac3c7f929cae3460abf23cab","tid":188245,"uid":99536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T07:52:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>本來應該有好多agent想pm你<br />\n<br />\n但見你唔要儲蓄plan<br />\n<br />\n我諗佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同問，呢排諗緊買保險，但同事都話買醫療就夠<br />\n<br />\n佢地話儲蓄係廢既，而保險佬係靠儲蓄plan食佣，想知多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你唔想agent有佣賺  又想agent service你 都幾矛盾<img src=\"/as